in airport departure and arrival areas and a range money changing kiosks including some operated by indonesian banks such as bni, bca and mandiri are available at the airport. most atms for international arriving passengers are available right after exiting customs. there is one atm to the immediate left of the customs exit, and another one a short walk away; near a restaurant. security protocols including passenger and baggage screening are similar to other large international airports in the region. limitations similar to those in the eu and us are placed upon the carrying of fluids and other so- called 